### Global variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api
@studentId = demo_student

### 1. Start Marathon
POST {{baseUrl}}/start-marathon
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "examName": "GATE CS 2025",
  "totalDays": 14,
  "hoursPerDay": 3,
  "syllabus": ["Operating Systems", "DBMS", "Algorithms", "Computer Networks"]
}

### 2. Get Today's Plan
GET {{baseUrl}}/today?studentId={{studentId}}

### 3. Generate Quiz
GET {{baseUrl}}/quiz/Operating%20Systems?difficulty=medium&questions=3

### 4. Submit Quiz
# Note: Use IDs from the generated quiz in step 3
POST {{baseUrl}}/submit-quiz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "{{studentId}}",
  "day": 1,
  "topic": "Operating Systems",
  "quizData": {
    "questions": [
      { "id": 1, "correctAnswer": "A" },
      { "id": 2, "correctAnswer": "B" },
      { "id": 3, "correctAnswer": "C" }
    ]
  },
  "userAnswers": {
    "1": "B",
    "2": "A",
    "3": "C"
  },
  "timeSpent": 20
}

### 5. Get Performance
GET {{baseUrl}}/performance?studentId={{studentId}}&days=3

### 6. Reflect and Reschedule
POST {{baseUrl}}/reflect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "{{studentId}}"
}

### 7. Fast Forward (Demo Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/fast-forward
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "{{studentId}}"
}

### 8. Get Full Schedule
GET {{baseUrl}}/schedule?studentId={{studentId}}&from=1&to=14
